quote: No! Try not. Do, or do not. There is no try.
author: George Lucas,  The Star Wars Trilogy

quote: Never say never
author: Charles Dickens

quote: Knock yourself out... Or rather, don't.

quote: Please don't die.
author: Randy Pausch,  The Last Lecture

quote: Do not dare not to dare.

quote: Babe!

quote: Don't. Don't let's pretend when there's no one around.

quote: I don't mind making jokes, but I don't want to look like one.

quote: Ask us no questions and we’ll tell you no lies.

quote: Flatter me, and I may not believe you. Criticize me, and I may not like you. Ignore me, and I may not forgive you. Encourage me, and I will not forget you. Love me and I may be forced to love you.

quote: I don't want to be in love but you're makin' me

quote: If you do not love me I shall not be loved If I do not love you I shall not love.

quote: Who dares, win

quote: It don't do you no nevermind to tell nobody nothing.

quote: Promise me you'll never forget me because if I thought you would, I'd never leave.

quote: If I do not write to empty my mind, I go mad.

quote: Don’t spoil me with your lies, love me with your truth.

quote: But if I don’t think about love, I will be nothing.

quote: Honey! Bring down a copy of my will - and an eraser!

quote: let your haters be your motivators

quote: Do not go gentle.

quote: Ow, Todd? Ow?

quote: Interrupt your thoughts of "I should", with your action of doing.

quote: I want to love you without clutching, appreciate you without judging, join you without invading, invite you without demanding, leave you without guilt, criticize you without blaming, and help you without insulting. If I can have the same from you, then we can truly meet and enrich each other.

quote: I can't go on, I'll go on.
author: Samuel Beckett,  I Can't Go On, I'll Go On: A Samuel Beckett Reader
